replies.body:
Don't cry child, at least you have an existence beyond this. Between World of Warcraft, Overwatch, League and Pokemon I've become a shell of a man. 

At least I can take pride in my knowledge.

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}

EDIT: No actually I can't, because I know Jaredan, Loping Cinder, WAAARGHbobo, ThermalKitten, FauxShizzle, Ant in Oz, Carnival Knights and the rest of Narrative are scoffing and chuckling at my feeble attempts to discern the lore.

{{sticker:zombie-nunu-tears}} 

Narrative are cruel and vindictive gods. Hopefully my attempts at comprehending the lore are worthy offerings to them.
